title: Sawbones: Vaping
description:
On Sawbones, we like to take a lot of hard lines and make grand proclamations: Vaccines good, viruses bad, that sort of thing. But when it comes to vaping, things get a little ... cloudier?

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
